_json.title: I Quit Social Media: Starting Fresh, Living Simply
_json.gridTitle: I Quit Social Media: Starting Fresh, Living Simply
_json.description: The day I hit delete, I sat with my empty space in the silence and smiled.This new found freedom and happiness has been met with more time and a higher vibration for love, kindness and life. I can hear my own voice and thoughts once again. I feel more confident, creative and excited about life. I control how I feel, what I read and what I watch. I am finally 100% focused on what I love and what brings me joy. #simplelife #simpleliving #freshliving #simplicity #simplelifestyle
